      Constructor for Reservation object
      Parameters:
      reservationStatus - identifies the status of the reservation (CONFIRMED, CHECKED_IN, CHECKED_OUT, EXPIRED, CANCELLED)
      reservationNum - uniquely identifies the reservation
      guestId - uniquely identifies the guest that is related to the reservation
      roomId - uniquely identifies the room that is related to the reservation
      checkIn - the date at which the guest checks in
      checkOut - the date at which the guest checks out
      numOfAdults - the number of adults in the room
      numOfChilden - the number of children in the room
